The Sydney Morning Herald described the game as an "emphatic derby win" for Sydney FC, while Sportskeeda provided betting tips and predictions for the match. The match brought together rivals despite the heated derby atmosphere, with the Sydney Morning Herald observing that some players had played golf together during the week. Sydney FC's winning streak in the derby now stands at four, and the club announced roster updates through its "Ins & Outs" feature. Yahoo Sport Australia highlighted Ouahim's performance as a "super sub" in the Sky Blues' victory.
